I saw this article and decided to share it with you ; 
This is not a momentary impulse , but rather a warm kindheartedness that has long existed in the heart . 
I asked myself what I would do if it were me . 
The answer is very clear . I would way , " You have the wrong number " and hang up the telephone . 
I 've been thinking all this year about how one can actually help someone . 
